{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1977,"month":9,"day":2}],"page_start":3,"page_end":3,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"欢呼呵，伟大的里程碑","authors":["杜志民"],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"咚！咚！咚！咚！……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"处处响着欢庆的喜鼓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嚓！嚓！嚓！嚓！……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"处处举起欢快的脚步；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"隆重地欢庆呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党的第十一次代表大会、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第十一届一中全会胜利闭幕！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纵情歌唱呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党的历史上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巍巍然一座里程碑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在我们心中高高矗！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢呼里程碑呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"激情溢满肺腑："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢呼新胜利呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们心潮起伏！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难忘怀，一九七六年——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"导师长辞我们去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"神州无处不痛哭……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刹时间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九天月动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五洋鳖浮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王张江姚反党集团，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妄图把红旗的颜色改涂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命的航船，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎样继续远航？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红色的大地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎样续描绚丽蓝图？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"动乱之际，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"危难之间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华主席继承毛主席遗志，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"率亿万军民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一举荡平了“四人帮”的魔窟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因此呵，祖国走向大治才"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有了宽敞的大路；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因此呵，历时十一年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第一次无产阶级文化大革命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才宣告胜利结束。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十一年大浪淘沉沙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十一年春阳照征途；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东思想大普及，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席旗帜迎风舞……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因此呵，才有这——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"承先启后，继往开来的大会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光焰昭日月，丰碑高高筑！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱呀，唱不尽的胜利歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绘呀，绘不赢的跃进图！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢呼里程碑呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顿觉眼前霞光铺；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢呼新胜利呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倍感心上春风抚！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华主席的政治报告呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"字字如珠玑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"声声扣心鼓："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席继续革命伟大理论，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照亮了我们前进的征途。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席的伟大旗帜呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"涤荡了“四人帮”的妖风毒雾。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东思想的阳光，洒遍了——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大江小河，四海五湖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上层建筑，经济基础……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抓纲治国的战斗号令，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"引导我们新的进军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"引导我们新的征途，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跃进！再跃进！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"加速！再加速！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向着四个现代化的目标，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"擂响震天的进军鼓！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，党的十一大呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——伟大的里程碑！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席旗帜的光辉照耀着你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你在我党的历史上高矗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你在八亿人民心中高矗！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十里长街华灯亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳光灿烂照首都，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花雨缤纷头顶洒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京城处处响爆竹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"首都的欢呼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和祖国冬地的欢呼连在一起。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高炉在欢呼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢水正滚沸！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田野在欢呼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遍山丰收谷！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军营在欢呼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"报靶红旗舞！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢呼呵，欢呼！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八亿人紧跟华主席为首的党中央，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜利大进军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昂首迈阔步！"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"name":"四人帮","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}